DOC.brief_summary: To evaluate the effects of food intake on plasma concentration of Z-338 in healthy volunteers.
DOC.brief_title: Effect of Food Intake on Pharmacokinetic Profiles of Z-338
DOC.detailed_description: The purpose of the study is to evaluate the influence of food intake on the pharmacokinetic profiles of Z-338 in healthy volunteers by a 3-way cross-over method.
DOC.criteria: Healthy subject Body weight: 50.0 80.0 kg BMI: 17.6 26.4 Receiving an investigational new drug within 120 days of the study Receiving medical treatment drugs within 7 days of the study Blood donation before the study
